"""
AO2 sdd-planner claude provider shim.

Reads an `ao2.sdd-provider-request.v1` JSON envelope on stdin, invokes the
real Claude Code CLI in --print/--output-format=json mode with the §8.3
system prompt + envelope context, then prints the extracted
`ao2.sdd-plan-candidate.v1` JSON object on stdout.

OAuth path — no ANTHROPIC_API_KEY required. Uses the user's existing
Claude Code session.

Logs every invocation (envelope, args, raw response, parsed candidate)
under /tmp/sdd-planner-claude-shim/logs/ for postmortem.
"""

